i need a southern drawl how help i decided on a huckleberry finn monolgue but i can't get the accent help the most helpful piece of advice i was ever offered for this type of accent is to use a slightly exaggerated american accent and then imagine the letters are all leaning into each other simple visualisation that really worked for me watch dr phil see the movie midnight in the garden of good and evil weird little film but great accents try and place your voice very high into the nasal cavity until you can feel your sinuses vibrating slightly use a lot of up and down jaw and lip movements drag out vowel sounds drop most of the t sounds eg the word got becomes ga' talk slowly not slow mo just a little slower than you normally do there's a lot more to it than that but that should be a start The Beach Boys University of Southern California Social rule Shit One Tree Hill (TV series) Kodocha Drama The Supremes University of California, Santa Barbara Petula Clark Lauren Bacall Pitaten Blonde on Blonde Trailer Park Boys The Adventures of Pete & Pete Transactional analysis The Contender (television series) Cleveland Browns $ale of the Century Barbra Streisand Wild at Heart (Buffy episode) Hollywood blacklist Futurama (TV series - season 3) Pittsburgh Steelers Game show Jon Secada Humphrey Bogart Cliff Richard Poker jargon Economic inequality 2000 Australian Grand Prix Ra (board game) Emerson College ELO rating system Henry Fonda Knots Landing Bing Crosby Cyndi Lauper Big Brother (USA TV series) Liam Gallagher Diablo II: Lord of Destruction Laura Schlessinger The Sims 2: University The Beatles bootlegs Georgetown University 2004 Republican National Convention DC Comics Prostate cancer EastEnders IBM PC compatible Kimi Finster Jennifer Lopez Monty Hall problem RuneScape Sam Barry Halle Berry Billboard Hot 100 Sounds of Summer: The Very Best of The Beach Boys New York Knicks Joke Democratic Party (United States) Education in the United States Hulk Hogan Procrastination Sharo